Begin by understanding your prescription, which includes details like sphere, cylinder, and axis, to accurately select the right lenses. Choose a reputable online eyewear retailer with positive customer reviews, as this reflects the reliability of both product quality and service. Explore the website's user-friendly interface, which should provide a variety of frame styles, materials, and sizes to suit your preferences. Look for virtual try-on tools or accurate measurement guides to assist in selecting frames that complement your face shape. Verify the return policy, warranty, and customer support options to guarantee assistance if issues arise. Lastly, prioritize eyeglasses that not only meet your visual needs but also align with your personal style. By paying attention to these details, you can confidently make an informed purchase of eyeglasses from the comfort of your home.

request.description:
This API endpoint makes an HTTP GET request to retrieve zip code information for admin purposes. The request should be sent to http://localhost:2000/api/admin/zip_code/get with the following payload in the raw request body:
```json
{
  "id":"",
  "status":""
}
```
The response will have a status code of 200 and a content type of application/json. The response body will contain a message, data array with zip code details, success status, and a status code.

The response structure will be as follows:
- message: A message related to the response
- data: An array containing zip code details including id, country code, country, zip codes, status, creation date, and update date
- success: Indicates the success status of the request
- statusCode: A status code indicating the result of the request

Example response:
```json
{
  "message":"",
  "data":[
    {
      "id":0,
      "country_code":"",
      "country":"",
      "zipcodes":[0],
      "status":"",
      "created_at":"",
      "updated_at":""
    }
  ],
  "success":true,
  "statusCode":0
}
```
